title: REPORT ON YSS NATIONAL PREPAREDNESS TRAINING PROGRAMME 2015 (Universiti Islam Antarabangsa Malaysia)
text: ( Source : Universiti Islam Antarabangsa Malaysia ) On 15th October - 18th October 2015 , Students Volunteers Foundation or YSS has been organized a training programme on flood relief management in collaboration with Jabatan Pertahanan Awam
